<h2>Location</h2>
<p>We will be in the group campsite at Flat Canyon Campground. It's 70 miles (1 hr 15 min drive) from my apartment, so likely similar for most of you. We have plenty of picnic tables, some grills, and a fire pit. We also have a bathroom to ourselves about 50 feet from the site. There are a few trees for hammocking, but I would recommend having other plans for sleeping just in case too many people bring hammocks. More info in the <a href="#what-to-bring">What to Bring</a> section below.</p>
